high_descs: Turn right, hang a left at the counter and walk to the counter ahead.
Pick up the white mug to the right of the toaster on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the white stove on the right.
Put the mug inside the microwave in front of the apples, heat it for a few seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, hang a right at the wall and walk to the counter ahead.
Put the heated mug on the platform of the coffee maker on the left side of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug on a coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk to the counter to the right of the stove with the toaster on it.
Pick up the mug to the right of the toaster on the counter.
Move to the front of the stove on the left and look up at the microwave above the stove.
Place the mug in the microwave, heat the mug, take the mug out of the microwave, and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the counter on the other side of the room with the coffee maker on it.
Put the mug in the coffee maker.
